gameModes.title: Game Modes
gameModes.content: Here is a list of modes available for finding a game. You can select several modes at once! To search for a 5v5 game, you need to win the training against bots.

party.title: Group
party.content: Here is your group: to invite a friend, click '+'

onlineStats.content: Here you can see how many players are currently playing and how many are simply online

chat.title: General Chat
chat.content: General chat for all players — here you can report problems, and you'll get help.

searchButton.title: Search Button
searchButton.content: When you choose a mode to search, press this button — the search for a game will begin.

adblock.title: Ad Block
adblock.content: Please disable ad blocking on this site. Although the game is completely free here, running the project still costs money. Have a great game!

seo.title: Queue
seo.description: Game search page for Classic Dota. Play in a group with your friends, bots, and other players
